</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-26_ pf-text-1">Immediate initiation of BLS can double or even triple the chances of survival for cardiac arrest victims.






















































</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eWfVMQ iFMXsG pf-28_ pf-text-1">Despite its critical importance, studies indicate that only a minority of the population is trained in BLS techniques.

























































